  "title": "We're gathered here, O Lord, as Thy one Body",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "We're gathered"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "here, O Lord, as Thy one"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "Body:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though we be"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "many,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "yet we"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "all are"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "one."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We share Thy life and own that we are"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "members,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And thus with"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "in, in"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "life we"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "all are"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "one."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is one Body"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "in this"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "uni"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "verse,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we ex"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "press"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "it here"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "on"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "earth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We stand as one in"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "text": "each locali"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "ty"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For all to"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "see,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D7",
              "text": "for all"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "to"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is one loaf, the symbol of Thy body:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "'Twas broken so that all the saints may share."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We eat this bread and, as we are partaking,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our actual oneness with all saints declare."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is one Body in this universe,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we express it here on earth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We stand as one in each locality"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For all to see, for all to see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One bread, one cup are now upon the table,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Showing that we can be naught else but one."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ has redeemed us, made us His own Body:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What can we say but, \"Amen, Lord, we're one!\""
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is one Body in this universe,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we express it here on earth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We stand as one in each locality"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For all to see, for all to see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We stand as one, and cannot be divided,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Because our oneness is of Christ alone."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We eat as one: one loaf, one cup partaking,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And thus our oneness visibly is shown."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is one Body in this universe,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we express it here on earth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We stand as one in each locality"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For all to see, for all to see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, what a joy to have this blessed oneness!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We sense that Thou, O Lord, art satisfied;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we too share this blissful satisfaction—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sweet foretaste of the Bridegroom with His Bride."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
